### Read all business partners
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/BusinessPartners
Authorization: Basic admin:admin

### Filter by last name
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/BusinessPartners?$filter=LastName eq 'Chen'
Authorization: Basic admin:admin

### Select specific fields
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/BusinessPartners?$select=BusinessPartner,BusinessPartnerFullName
Authorization: Basic admin:admin

### Search
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/BusinessPartners?$filter=contains(LastName, 'Garcia')
Authorization: Basic admin:admin

### Top N with ordering
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/BusinessPartners?$orderby=BusinessPartnerFullName desc&$top=3
Authorization: Basic admin:admin

### Read speakers — should include businessPartnerFullName from S/4HANA
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Speakers?$select=firstName,lastName,businessPartner,businessPartnerFullName
Authorization: Basic admin:admin

### Read a single speaker with BP enrichment
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Speakers({{speakerId}})?$select=firstName,lastName,businessPartner,businessPartnerFullName
Authorization: Basic admin:admin

### Speakers without BP links — businessPartnerFullName should be null
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Speakers?$filter=businessPartner eq null
Authorization: Basic admin:admin

### Speakers with BP links — businessPartnerFullName should be populated
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Speakers?$filter=businessPartner ne null
Authorization: Basic admin:admin